description:
Sister Davis has tried to be a model of virtuousness. She was blessed with centerfold
looks but has stayed pure and true. Even when she was on her mission, she did not let
the sinful ways of the world affect her. The Seed Bearer has called her to his office and
she has no idea what for. But she knows that when he asks you to do something, you
must obey.
title: Sister Davis: The Calling
